      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SLICK RAZOR (1) missed the frame last time out when sixth at this track from Box seven (30.36) but draws same box here as latest win. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. ASCEND FERN (2) had won two in a row before finishing fourth (29.97) last time at Richmond. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Should be about the mark. ENTERTAINER (7) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at four of 14 starts including six wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (30.22) over 520m at this track. Form here sound including three wins. Has the ability and rates a key chance this line-up. SPRING WITNESS (4) has been in the placings at his last two runs, most recently when third (29.78) in a Grade 4/5 over 520m at this track. Good beginner who will be prominent from trap two.",
